{"tid":1289198,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於「畫家」這個人","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:25:20.000Z","uid":203273,"like":166,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ea08ac104f1a6bd30e20d8829f628d2f7cafbc79","tid":1289198,"uid":203273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"黃洋達:<br />\n關於「畫家」這個人：<br />\n以前佔領旺角，每一晚都會有爛仔、藍絲落嚟佔領區搞事！畫家一見有交嗌，就會衝過去鬧人，向藍絲大聲呼喝：「屌你老母啦！左膠！」<br />\n<br />\n因為佔領區有好多「提防左膠」嘅海報，畫家一直以為「左膠」就即係「共產黨」、「建制派」。<br />\n我解釋畀佢聽，「左膠」其實係指嗰d出賣社運搞散運動嘅膠人，佢問返我，咁d「左膠」做過d咩呀？我約略講下關於「散水」、「搞大台」、「阻人抗爭」、「篤灰」之類的⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n跟住畫家就話啦：<br />\n「屌你老母！咁咪即係共產黨囉！」<br />\n<br />\n結論：畫家好喪、但畫家不是傻的！"},{"pid":"98fa526fb5506179c26ed52e9a1e5c6fc93743e6","tid":1289198,"uid":215417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0601687e6a7e355c00e38301660305af92b17cbe","tid":1289198,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":34,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/pw72u6Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw72u6Z.gif&h=1bec9fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你竟然話白卡唔係傻既？<br />\n咁劉馬車都係上帝啦<br />\n劉馬車叫林小姐參選架<br />\n老港女<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/pw72u6Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw72u6Z.gif&h=1bec9fff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f71bee4bfa6172f05e4a888d9979b23941e02a9e","tid":1289198,"uid":263485,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"佔旺3傻之一。"